work.name: University of Missouri System
work.summary: Worked as Graduate Research Assistant performing the duties of Database Programmer/Analyst at Application Development Network (ADN), DoIT which supports University of Missouri System faculty and students through agile and rapid creation of new applications.
highlights: Worked on .NET security features such as Form-Based Authentication and Role-Based Authorization.
Involved in bug fixes and production support.
Worked closely with Scrum Master for backlog catalogs, feature catalogs and prioritized the tasks

projects.name: AppInventory
